      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 73.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 73.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>勇於敢則殺，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He whose boldness appears in his daring (to do wrong, in defiance of the laws) is put to death; he whose boldness appears in his not daring (to do so) lives on.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-073__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-073</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 73.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 73.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>勇於不敢則活。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Of these two cases the one appears to be advantageous, and the other to be injurious.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-073__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
