      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 73.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天之所惡，孰知其故？是以聖人猶難之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When Heaven's anger smites a man,</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
